subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: The Australian Open’s defending champion Victoria Azarenka defeated the injured American Jamie Hampton, 6-4, 4-6, 6-2, and Serena Williams cruised past Ayumi Morita, 6-1, 6-3, to advance to the fourth round.
